OL,5, A woman secretly carried out an illegal
OL,6, pagan-style burial for her father after
OL,7, advising him not to seek medical help, 
OL,8, an inquest has heard.                  
OL,10,FEirys Brett suggested Donald Brett take
OL,11,Falternative medicines instead, but he  
OL,12,Fbecame "quite unwell" and died.        
OL,14,FMs Brett and her boyfriend then drove  
OL,15,Fthe 78-year-old's body to his home in  
OL,16,FPowys, leaving it propped on a chair   
OL,17,Ffor days while they dug a grave.       
OL,19,FAn open conclusion was recorded at     
OL,20,FPontypridd Coroner's Court.            
